NetDAG — The Problem
Blockchain adoption remains limited outside financial speculation.
Major barriers include:
• complex wallets and gas fees • lack of real-world utility • supply chain counterfeiting • poor user experience
Consumers and businesses need simple and trusted verification systems for real-world products.


NetDAG — The Opportunity
Global counterfeit trade exceeds $550B annually.     
Consumers increasingly demand:
• product authenticity verification • transparent supply chains • trusted digital infrastructure
Blockchain can provide trust, but most projects focus only on financial transactions.
The next wave of blockchain adoption will come from real-world utility.


NetDAG — The NetDAG Solution
NetDAG is building a blockchain ecosystem designed to extend blockchain technology into everyday economic activity.
The platform integrates:
• DAG-based transaction architecture • gasless user access • AI-driven security (Guardian layer) • product authenticity verification through the Provenance dApp
NetDAG enables consumers to verify products simply by scanning a product code.


